Field

Description

Available balance

Real-time balance value of the bank account.

Currency

Currency of the bank account. Required.

Multicurrency enabled

Whether the bank account supports multicurrency operations.

Opened on

Date when the bank account was opened.

Activated on

Date when the bank account was activated.

Closed on

Date when the bank account was locked or closed. Visible only for "Locked" or "Closed" statuses.

Reason for lock/closure

Required reason if the bank account is locked or closed. Visible only for "Locked" or "Closed" statuses.
